This is a simple user script for Google Chrome that removes articles about ABB from the frontpage of norwegian online news papers.
The sites are still not "ABB-free", but there should be minimal exposure to ABB on the supported sites.

Contributors are welcome, the repository for the project is open for editing.

Currently supported sites:
vg.no
aftenposten.no
bt.no
tv2.no
nrk.no

Installation:
- Click and download the following link in Google Chrome: https://github.com/nso/AbbBlocker/raw/master/AbbBlocker.user.js
- Open the downloaded file (click the file in Google Chrome to open it)
- Accept the Extension installation
- Done
